WEBVTT

00:00:00.329 --> 00:00:04.208
So I would like to discuss
about meditation.

00:00:04.959 --> 00:00:06.502
But first of all,

00:00:06.502 --> 00:00:09.297
I'd like to ask you
a very simple question.

00:00:10.590 --> 00:00:12.050
Can you see my hand?

00:00:12.717 --> 00:00:14.427
Yes, raise your hand.

00:00:14.427 --> 00:00:15.595
Audience: Yes.

00:00:15.636 --> 00:00:17.764
Yongey Mingyur Rinpoche:
OK, can you hear me?

00:00:17.764 --> 00:00:18.890
Audience: Yes.

00:00:19.348 --> 00:00:20.516
YMR: Yes?

00:00:21.100 --> 00:00:22.477
Great.

00:00:22.477 --> 00:00:24.145
That is the meditation.

00:00:24.645 --> 00:00:25.772
So, finished.

00:00:26.189 --> 00:00:27.565
My TED Talk is finished.

00:00:27.607 --> 00:00:30.526
(Laughter and applause)